On january 11, 2010
[993635]
FAQ there is theme about that. Direct Copy->Paste

To get the pearl first you have to combat against the Water Elemental at the university and kill him. Once you beat it, you will obtain the swimming buoy, with that you will be able to cross swiming from the Frish Port to the Islands.

There you have to go to the "Mutant Falls" and talk with Master Hydargol, he will ask you about a waterlily pad, then you have to go back to the Frish Port and talk with the monk, he will give you the waterlily pad (another status). Return to the Mutants Falls and give the waterlily to Hydargol, and finally he will give you the pearl.

With the pearl, all your Dinoz will recover 5 at 00:00 (web's clock) if they are at the fountain of youth.

-edit-
When you received this Pearl, it will appear on your account page and not in your inventory!
